{
  "_comment": "WATI multimedia → texto. Equivalente al Switch de texto/audio/imagen pero adaptado a WATI. Enrutar por tipo de mensaje; audio se transcribe (Whisper), imagen se describe (GPT-4o-mini), y todo se normaliza a un único campo `message`. Pegar después del nodo que mapea el payload de WATI (en tu flujo: 'Edit Fields').",
  "_requisitos": [
    "1. En tu nodo 'Edit Fields' (el que mapea body.* del webhook WATI) AGREGÁ dos campos string:",
    "      media_link  =  {{ $json.body.data }}        (ruta/nombre del archivo que manda WATI)",
    "      media_mime  =  {{ $json.body.type }}        (opcional, para debug)",
    "   Sin 'media_link' los nodos de descarga no saben qué bajar.",
    "2. Los 2 nodos 'Descargar...' ya usan variables de entorno. Configurá en n8n:",
    "      WATI_SERVER = https://live-mt-server.wati.io/<TENANT_ID>   (sin barra final)",
    "      WATI_TOKEN  = <tu token de WATI>",
    "   Tienen timeout de 20s y 3 reintentos automáticos.",
    "3. Verificá que las credenciales OpenAI ('SONNER - OpenAi account' o la del proyecto) estén seleccionadas en Transcribir/Analyze.",
    "4. Conectá la salida de tu Switch/mapper a 'Switch Tipo (WATI)', y la salida de 'Normalizar mensaje' a lo que siga (agente / logger)."
  ],
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rules": {
          "values": [
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": { "caseSensitive": true, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict", "version": 2 },
                "conditions": [
                  { "id": "w-cond-text", "leftValue": "={{ $json.tipo_de_mensaje }}", "rightValue": "text", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "Texto"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": { "caseSensitive": true, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict", "version": 2 },
                "conditions": [
                  { "id": "w-cond-audio", "leftValue": "={{ $json.tipo_de_mensaje }}", "rightValue": "audio", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "Audio"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": { "caseSensitive": true, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict", "version": 2 },
                "conditions": [
                  { "id": "w-cond-image", "leftValue": "={{ $json.tipo_de_mensaje }}", "rightValue": "image", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "Imagen"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": { "fallbackOutput": "extra", "renameFallbackOutput": "Otro" }
      },
      "id": "wati-switch-001",
      "name": "Switch Tipo (WATI)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
      "position": [200, 400],
      "typeVersion": 3.2,
      "notes": "Enruta por tipo_de_mensaje (= body.type de WATI). WATI usa: text | image | audio | video | document."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            { "id": "wt-text", "name": "text", "value": "={{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.mensaje }}", "type": "string" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [440, 280],
      "id": "wati-obtener-texto",
      "name": "Obtener Texto (WATI)"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.WATI_SERVER }}/api/v1/getMedia?fileName={{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.media_link }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env.WATI_TOKEN }}" }
          ]
        },
        "options": { "timeout": 20000, "response": { "response": { "responseFormat": "file" } } }
      },
      "id": "wati-descargar-audio",
      "name": "Descargar Audio (WATI)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "position": [440, 460],
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000,
      "notes": "Usa $env.WATI_SERVER (ej. https://live-mt-server.wati.io/<TENANT_ID>) y $env.WATI_TOKEN. Timeout 20s + 3 reintentos."
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "resource": "audio", "operation": "transcribe", "options": {} },
      "id": "wati-transcribir-audio",
      "name": "Transcribir Audio (WATI)",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "position": [660, 460],
      "typeVersion": 1.5,
      "credentials": { "openAiApi": { "id": "TpgS7MbojkKQfXYq", "name": "SONNER - OpenAi account" } }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            { "id": "wa-audio-wrap", "name": "content", "type": "string", "value": "=<audio>\n  {{ $json.text }}\n</audio>" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "wati-obtener-mensaje-audio",
      "name": "Obtener Mensaje Audio (WATI)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "position": [880, 460],
      "typeVersion": 3.4
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.WATI_SERVER }}/api/v1/getMedia?fileName={{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.media_link }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env.WATI_TOKEN }}" }
          ]
        },
        "options": { "timeout": 20000, "response": { "response": { "responseFormat": "file" } } }
      },
      "id": "wati-descargar-imagen",
      "name": "Descargar Imagen (WATI)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "position": [440, 640],
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000,
      "notes": "Usa $env.WATI_SERVER (ej. https://live-mt-server.wati.io/<TENANT_ID>) y $env.WATI_TOKEN. Timeout 20s + 3 reintentos."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "image",
        "operation": "analyze",
        "modelId": { "__rl": true, "value": "gpt-4o-mini", "mode": "list", "cachedResultName": "GPT-4O-MINI" },
        "text": "Describe la imagen en detalle. Si contiene texto, transcribilo. Si es relevante para un seguro o trámite (póliza, DNI, comprobante de pago, formulario, captura de chat), describí qué es y extraé los datos clave.",
        "inputType": "base64",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.8,
      "position": [660, 640],
      "id": "wati-analyze-imagen",
      "name": "Analyze Imagen (WATI)",
      "credentials": { "openAiApi": { "id": "TpgS7MbojkKQfXYq", "name": "SONNER - OpenAi account" } }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            { "id": "wa-img-wrap", "name": "content", "value": "=<image>\n {{ $json.content }}\n</image>", "type": "string" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [880, 640],
      "id": "wati-imagen-a-texto",
      "name": "Imagen a Texto (WATI)"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.noOp",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [440, 820],
      "id": "wati-otro-ignorar",
      "name": "Otro tipo (ignorar)"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const item = $input.first().json;\nconst message = item.Content || item.content || item.text || item.message || \"\";\nif (!message) {\n  // No tiramos error (cortaría el flujo); avisamos con un placeholder para que\n  // el agente pueda responder algo y queda registrado en los logs.\n  console.warn('Normalizar mensaje: no se encontro contenido', JSON.stringify(item).slice(0, 300));\n  return [{ json: { message: '[mensaje no reconocido]', _empty: true } }];\n}\nreturn [{ json: { message } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1120, 400],
      "id": "wati-normalizar",
      "name": "Normalizar mensaje"
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Switch Tipo (WATI)": {
      "main": [
        [ { "node": "Obtener Texto (WATI)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ],
        [ { "node": "Descargar Audio (WATI)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ],
        [ { "node": "Descargar Imagen (WATI)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ],
        [ { "node": "Otro tipo (ignorar)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ]
      ]
    },
    "Obtener Texto (WATI)": { "main": [ [ { "node": "Normalizar mensaje", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ] ] },
    "Descargar Audio (WATI)": { "main": [ [ { "node": "Transcribir Audio (WATI)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ] ] },
    "Transcribir Audio (WATI)": { "main": [ [ { "node": "Obtener Mensaje Audio (WATI)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ] ] },
    "Obtener Mensaje Audio (WATI)": { "main": [ [ { "node": "Normalizar mensaje", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ] ] },
    "Descargar Imagen (WATI)": { "main": [ [ { "node": "Analyze Imagen (WATI)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ] ] },
    "Analyze Imagen (WATI)": { "main": [ [ { "node": "Imagen a Texto (WATI)", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ] ] },
    "Imagen a Texto (WATI)": { "main": [ [ { "node": "Normalizar mensaje", "type": "main", "index": 0 } ] ] },
    "Normalizar mensaje": { "main": [ [] ] }
  },
  "pinData": {},
  "meta": { "templateCredsSetupCompleted": true }
}
